<article class="module intro">
	<section class="content">
		<section class="title">
			<h1>Victor Herrera</h1>
			<ul>
				<li>Software Engineer Lead</li>
				<li>Senior Web Developer</li>
				<li>Die-hard Gamer</li>
			</ul>
			<nav>
				<ul fade-in>
					<li>
						<a href="#about" class="about"></a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="#work" class="work"></a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="#contact" class="contact"></a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</nav>
		</section>
		<figure>
			<img src="/img/intro/vh.png" alt="VH" fade-in="self" />
		</figure>
	</section>
</article>
<article id="about" class="module about reduced" ng-controller="about">
	<section class="content" fade-in="self">
		<h2>About Me</h2>
		<article>
			<header class="code">
				<h3>Dem Skillz</h3>
			</header>
			{{> stats meters=data.skills}}
		</article>
		<article>
			<header class="game">
				<h3>Personal Interests</h3>
			</header>
			{{> stats meters=data.likes}}
		</article>
	</section>
</article>
<article id="work" class="module work reduced" ng-controller="work">
	<section class="content" fade-in="self">
		<h2>My Work</h2>
		<p>I&rsquo;ve worked mostly on private companies and under strict NDAs, therefore I am not under the liberty to divulge my participation on a public/personal site. However I can say that it has been often for highly scalable applications which demand the best standards and practices. Also here&rsquo;s a list of the places I&rsquo;ve work on as well as some simple code samples from my github profile. Still, I believe this site to be perfectly capable of showing my mad skillz on ze coding.</p>
		<article>
			<section class="companies">
				{{#each data.works}}
					<div data-animation="scale-fade">
						<h3>{{name}}</h3>
						<h4 ng-click="toggle($event)">{{position}}</h4>
						<ul>
							{{#each responsibilities}}
								<li>{{this}}</li>
							{{/each}}
						</ul>
					</div>
				{{/each}}
			</section>
			<section class="samples" data-animation="slide-down">
				<ul>
					{{#each data.samples}}
					<li data-fade-in>
						<a href="{{url}}">
							<figure data-slide-down>
								<img src="{{image.filename}}" alt="GitHub Profile" />
								<figcaption>{{project}}</figcaption>
							</figure>
						</a>
					</li>
					{{/each}}
				</ul>
			</section>
		</article>
	</section>
</article>
<article id="contact" class="module contact reduced">
	<section class="content" fade-in="self">
		<h2>Contact Me</h2>

		<form>
			<fieldset>
				<legend>Don&rsquo;t be shy to reach out. What can I do for you?</legend>
				<div>
					<section class="info">
						<div class="field">
							<label for="">Name</label>
							<input type="text" />
						</div>
						<div class="field">
							<label for="">Email</label>
							<input type="text" />
						</div>
					</section>
					<section class="message">
						<div class="field">
							<label for="">Message</label>
							<textarea></textarea>
						</div>
					</section>
				</div>
				<section class="send">
					<button>Send</button>
				</section>
			</fieldset>
			<figure>
				<img src="/img/contact/mail.png" alt="Mail" />
			</figure>
		</form>
	</section>
</article>